Chipotle: The Complete History in About Three Minutes

   2:42 PM EST
   February 2, 2016
   [86]Share on Facebook[87]Share on Twitter[88]Share on WhatsApp
   [89]Share on LinkedIn[90]Share on Reddit[91]Share on
   Google+[92]E-mail[93]Share on Twitter[94]Share on WhatsApp

Chipotle was founded in Denver in 1993 and grew to be one of the most
successful fast-food companies ever. This video explains how Chipotle founder
Steve Ells turned his love of burritos into a chain of about 500 restaurants
over the past twenty years. (video by Max Rosen, Jed Rosenberg, Victoria
Blackburne-Daniell)

