   Verizon-Yahoo Deal?: Bloomberg West (Full Show 02/08)
   February 8, 2016
   Startups Focus on Profit to Raise Funds
   34:02 - Mehul Patel, chief executive officer at Hired, discusses his
   latest round of fund raising and his outlook for the company. He speaks
   to Bloomberg's Emily Chang on "Bloomberg West." (Source: Bloomberg)
